The paper proposes a face detection method based on convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The method also involves the extraction of discriminative features, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the efficiency and effectiveness of the proposed method, which are important considerations in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Finally, the use of neural networks for feature extraction and classification is a common topic in neural networks (cs.NE).
